schen Disziplingeschichte, wendet ihn exemplarisch an und zeigt Perspektiven auf, wie damit theorie- und methodikbezogene Herausforderungen in der Religionswissenschaft produktiv angegangen werden können.  aThis study shows that not only are religious studies »beyond religion« possible, but that in concert with other related academic discourses, the discipline can actually be strengthened.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aReligionssoziologie. 4aReligionswissenschaft. 4aRussell McCutcheon. 4aSoziorhetorik. 4aTheorie. 7aRELIGION / General.2bisacsh  aReligious Studies.  aRussell McCutcheon.  aSociology of Religion.  aTheory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2015 Part 2z978311076664608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383763138840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839431382?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839431382423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839431382/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076664-6  DG Plus PP Package 2015 Part 2b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016